text.tspan: Miss Petunia is Mister Pickles' favorite thing in the
whole wide world. You should have seen him when
she was born; he was squealing with excitement.
Sadly, their mother died during childbirth, leaving
Mister Pickles to care for his newborn sister on his
own. Fortunately, he is more than capable of doing so,
considering the fact that he can buy at least one extra
cat tree, and so he has almost no trouble taking care
of her. She has an uncanny ability to copy the voice of
other people, and really likes pumpkins. Also, she
LOVES Anastasia, and enjoys spending time with her,
watching her do whatever. Anastasia even gave her an
old witch hat! How sweet, right?
